UID:--UMHxAdQTtT1K4Rbvu3k
SUMMARY:Lauren Spencer Smith: THE ART OF BEING A MESS TOUR
DTSTAMP:20260324T020908Z
DTSTART:20260324T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:To further Lauren Spencer Smith's support of young people facin
	g housing insecurity\, hunger\, and addiction\, $1 per ticket will be paid
	 from Live Nation to PLUS1 for the Lauren Spencer Smith Fund\, supporting 
	organizations providing critical care and support. www.plus1.org No portio
	n of the ticket purchase is tax deductible. The Moore Theatre is located i
	n downtown Seattle at 1932 2nd Ave\, Seattle\, WA 98101. There is an overa
	ll 6 ticket limit per patron. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will have
	 their orders canceled at the venue's discretion. All sales are final. No 
	refunds or exchanges. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event.
	 Venue reserves the right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise not
	ed\, each person must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. 
	There is no elevator. Stairs only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors &
	 bag search at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/s
	afety There is no elevator. Stairs only to the balcony level. When purchas
	ing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email or ph
	one if any assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\;
	 you may reach us by email at accessibility@stgpresents.org or call us at 
	206-682-1414 ext. 5. Each accessible seat houses an armless freestanding c
	hair for patrons with mobility impairments and their companions. The frees
	tanding chair can be removed to accommodate a wheelchair.\n\nhttps://www.t
	icketmaster.com/lauren-spencer-smith-the-art-of-seattle-washington-03-23-2
	026/event/0F0062C2F4D03A7E\n\nFrom STG - Moore Theatre
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/lauren-spencer-smith-the-art-of-seattle-wa
	shington-03-23-2026/event/0F0062C2F4D03A7E
LOCATION:Moore Theatre\, 1932 2nd Ave\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:stg-moore
CATEGORIES:STG - Moore Theatre
